Syria to End 48-Year State of Emergency Within a Week, Assad Tells Cabinet

-- B y   I n a l   E r s a n
-- 
2011-04-16T15:17:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-16/syria-to-end-48-year-state-of-emergency-within-a-week-assad-tells-cabinet.html
Syria ’s President Bashar Assad said
the country’s state of emergency must be lifted by next week.  The Syrian leader’s comments were aired by state television
today after a new Cabinet was sworn in following weeks of unrest
in the country. Legislation was required to regulate protests,
he said.  The state of emergency has been in place for 48 years.  To contact the reporter on this story:
